<p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51)"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 24px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased">一、指导思想</span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 37px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 24px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased">根据</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased">教育部、江西省教育厅有关高职单招工作要求，结合我校实际，特制定江西软件职业技术大学</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased">202</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased">3</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased">年高职单独招生考试工作</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased">实施方案。</span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51)"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 24px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(34, 34, 34)"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">二、组织保证</span></span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px 0px 0px 40px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51)"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 24px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(34, 34, 34)"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 