list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 37px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 24px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(34, 34, 34)"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">高职单招工作领导小组，全面领导协调考试招生、考试各项工作</span></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(34, 34, 34)"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">，</span></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(34, 34, 34)"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">确保高职单招考试录取工作公平、公正、公开，确保招生考试安全有序实施。</span></span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: