bkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 37px"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 24px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(34, 34, 34)"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">具体负责高职单招招生考试各项工作组织实施和协调。为确保单招工作能够顺利进行，根据工作职能下设六个工作组：</span></span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51)"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 24px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(34, 34, 34)"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)">1.考务组：</span></span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px 0px 0px 40px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text