ne;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased">符合江西省普通高校招生考试报名条件并已取得江西省</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased">202</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased">3</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased">年普通高考报名资格的考生。</span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51)"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 24px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased">四</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased">、报名时间及方式：</span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51)"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 24px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased">&nbsp; &nbsp; （一）报名时间：</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased">3月</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased">7</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased">日</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased">9:00--3月</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased">9</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased">日</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased">17:00，逾期不予办理。</span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51)"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 24px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased">&nbsp; &nbsp; （二）报名方式：考生在规定时间内自行登陆省教育考试院网（网址</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased">www.jxeea.cn）“高职单招报考系统” ，</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased">签订《江西省</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased">2023年高职单招考试诚信报考承若书》，</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased">选报院校及专业，每位考生限报</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased">1所学校，可选报1至 5个专业及是否服从专业调剂。</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased">在规定的网报时间内，考生可以对所报考院校及专业修改</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased">1次。</span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51)"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 24px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased">五、</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased">资格审核：</span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px 0px 0px 40px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51)"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 24px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased">（一）</span>&nbsp;<span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased">现场确认时间：考生凭二代身份证原件于</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased">202</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased">3</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased">年</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased">3月</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased">17</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased">日</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased">前</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased">到校现场</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased">或网上</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased">确认</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased">参加考试</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased">，领取准考证、熟悉考场</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased">等。</span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px 0px 0px 40px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;color: rgb(51, 51, 51)"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 24px;font-family: 仿宋;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;color: rgb(86, 64, 89)"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 16px;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smooth